external_knowledge:
External knowledge is not explicitly required for this query, but it is assumed that the age categories are defined as follows: 
- Infant: 0-1 year old; 
- Child: 2-12 years old; 
- Teenager: 13-19 years old; 
- Young Adult: 20-29 years old; 
- Adult: 30-64 years old; 
- Senior: 65 and above.

sql:
SELECT AVG(fare_scaled) AS average_fare
FROM passengers
WHERE embarked_c = 1 AND age_categories_adult = 1;
